00:02.878 --> 00:05.380
Nine days

00:02.878 --> 00:05.380
past expiration.

00:08.300 --> 00:09.635
Ugh!

00:09.677 --> 00:11.094
Here.

00:14.473 --> 00:16.183
Ugh! Turned carbonated.

00:19.895 --> 00:22.940
Expired two months ago.

00:22.982 --> 00:25.484
You don't have the guts.

00:30.113 --> 00:31.991
(coughing)

00:38.747 --> 00:41.082
When was the last

00:38.747 --> 00:41.082
Christmas we had eggnog?

00:41.124 --> 00:42.918
I think before Dewey.

00:48.131 --> 00:49.717
It's all you, man.

00:50.718 --> 00:52.093
(gagging)

00:52.135 --> 00:54.972
This is a game that

00:52.135 --> 00:54.972
has no winners.

