♪ Yes, no, maybe ♪

00:58.308 --> 01:01.102
♪ I don't know ♪

01:01.144 --> 01:04.105
♪ Can you repeat the question? ♪

01:04.147 --> 01:06.274
♪ You're not the boss

01:04.147 --> 01:06.274
of me now ♪

