♪ You're not the boss

01:08.777 --> 01:11.196
of me now ♪

01:11.238 --> 01:13.323
♪ And you're not so big ♪

01:13.365 --> 01:15.784
♪ You're not the boss

01:13.365 --> 01:15.784
of me now ♪

